<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有吉姆在，大家更开心了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把学校里的事讲给孩子们听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，妈妈不用每天写故事了，于是她给孩子们上课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道铁路有没有想我们。”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们很久都没有向9点15分的火车挥手了。我们明天去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，他们来到栏杆边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看着9点15分的火车从隧道开出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我们的爱带给爸爸！”他们挥着手帕喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老先生也在窗口向他们挥手。这并不奇怪，因为他总是这样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是今天有一点儿不同。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个窗户都有人拿着手帕和报纸向他们挥手，并对他们微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”孩子们说，“为什么大家都向我们挥手？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能是老先生让大家挥手的。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>确实是这样！老先生早早就到火车站，拜托了每一位乘客。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乘客们有的很惊讶，有的很好奇，还有的怀疑或者生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是后来，乘客们都看到了报纸上的一篇文章，这让他们都很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，当他们看到孩子们时，就一起向他们挥手了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到家里，鲍比一直在想这件事，不能认真上课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈同意她提前离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去火车站和帕克斯聊聊。”鲍比想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车站里，好像每个人都拿着一份报纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个通常从不对她微笑的人，竟然在对她微笑！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真奇怪。”她想。帕克斯不知道在哪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，鲍比对火车站里的猫说：“今天大家都很友好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>11点54分的火车快要进站时，帕克斯出现了。他也拿着一份报纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！”他对鲍比说，“我看到报纸了，真为你高兴！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在报纸上看到什么了？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是11点54分的火车已经进站了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯看向每一个窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有三个人下了火车：第一个是拿着三个盒子的女人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二个是提着棕色行李箱的女人，第三个是……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！爸爸！我的爸爸！”鲍比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都把头伸出窗外，静静地看着这个高大但脸色苍白的男人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有紧紧抱着她的女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比觉得自己永远都不会放开爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上妈妈没有收到我的信吗？”爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上没有信。”鲍比说，“哦，爸爸，真的是你吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸握住她的手说：“现在没事了。他们抓住了真正的间谍。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都知道你不是间谍。”鲍比自豪地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们——我、妈妈和老先生一直都很确信。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。我得谢谢你的朋友。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸和鲍比一起走向他们的房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比先跑进去，想着该怎么告诉妈妈这个好消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在花园里等着，看着花园里漂亮的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>被关了这么久，每一朵花对他来说都是一个小奇迹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，鲍比打开门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快进来，爸爸。”她大喊，“欢迎回家！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>